nhc_headline: ...KELI HEADING WESTWARD WITH LITTLE CHANGE IN STRENGTH...
summary: ...KELI HEADING WESTWARD WITH LITTLE CHANGE IN STRENGTH... As of 11:00 AM HST Tue Jul 29 the center of Keli was located near 12.8, -149.9 with movement W at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1006 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 40 mph.
